parameters:
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] My leg is necrotizing. I don't know how much longer I can
live... you know.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] I could die at any moment.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Luna, because of my condition, I want to convey my feelings to
you.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] I've always loved you, Luna. Ever since we were little.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] But why did things turn out this way?

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] You, Becky, and I have served Lady Lucia. You've worked so hard
to be recognized by Lady Lucia.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] You honed your Blue magic to help Lady Lucia, and now you're
trying to use that same Blue magic to defeat her.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Sorry, but let me say this.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] I've been thinking about why you went through all the trouble
since you were little to become an Blue mage. You dedicated
everything to make Lady Lucia happy...

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] There was no princess more kind-hearted and caring for her
people than Lady Lucia. It wasn't just you; Becky and I also took
pride in guarding her.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] And now we all hate each other... It's just too sad...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I feel anger towards myself for ever admiring such a person.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Lucia killed her own mother and has been tormenting Noah and
everyone else using steel soldiers.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] She's formed an alliance with the magical kingdom of Valentia
and is always seen with those cruel Valentian generals.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] The generals of Valentia... You mean Hilda and Sylvia?

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] They're searching for villages of rebels. Recently, a village
was completely poisoned to death, apparently by Sylvia.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] The village of warriors we met in the forest today was also
brutally slaughtered by Hilda. It's all under Lucia's orders.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] So unless we defeat Lucia, Valentia won't back down, huh?

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] If Lady Lucia hadn't awakened as a direct-line mage, none of
this would have happened.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] A direct-line mage is one in billions. They are called the core
or mother and are worshipped. They are the aspiration and legend of
every mage.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Lucia has changed. She's become too distant, a being far too
special.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] More importantly, Noah, I'm thinking of looking for a medicine
to cure your leg. I'll ask the informant Jeff where it might be.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Yes, a medicine to stop the necrosis. I think there might be a
new drug if we go to the imperial capital Jupiterino, but we're part
of the resistance so we can't go there. That's why I'm thinking of
looking for the ingredients for the medicine.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] The ingredients for the medicine... Luna, thank you.
\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] Noah, with that bad leg of yours, are you on a date?

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] What do you want? Are you still trying to make Luna your
mistress? She hates sleazy men like you.
\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] Well, we won't know unless we ask Luna, right?

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] No. Dalieh, just like Noah said. I don't like people who treat
women as toys. I will never become one of your playthings.
\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] Is that so, is that so. You two seem to get along well.

\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] More importantly, Noah, if you stay here with that bad leg,
the village chief will scold you, right? You're using the village's
money for treatment. Why don't you head back soon?
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Ugh... I know. Luna, go on ahead without me.

\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] Luna, I've come to like you. I have many mistresses, but none
as innocent as you. And surprisingly, your breasts and butt look big.

\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] Luna, I want to make you mine before Noah does. I want to see
the frustrated look on Noah's face when I take you from him.

\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] Luna, a boring man like Noah doesn't suit you. If you were
with me, I'd make you feel good, and you'd melt just like my other
mistresses.
\C[31][Dalieh]\C[0] That's too bad. But I will definitely make you mine.

Although Luna rejected Dalieh's advances, she was strongly ordered by
the village chief to work at the brothel. It was Dalieh who had
reported today's events to his father, the village chief.
For now, Luna and the others headed towards the informant.
\I[84] You can now work at the brothelNight.

\I[84] To work at the brothel, you need to progress the game further. Once
the conditions are met, you can work there. Let's move the game
forward.

\I[84] By working at the brothel, other erotic events will be unlocked. To
trigger other erotic events, you must work at the brothel first.
